Privacy Policy
Information Collection
1. Personal Information:
Definition
: “Personal Information” refers to data that can identify you as an individual. This includes, but is not limited to, your name, email address, physical address, calendar entries, contact entries, files, and photos.
Collection
: We do
NOT
collect any personal information about you. Our watch face applications are designed to function without the need for any personally identifiable information.
Usage
: As we do not collect personal information, there is no usage or storage of such data. We ensure that your identity and personal details remain private and protected.
2. Non-Personal Information:
Definition
: “Non-Personal Information” refers to data that cannot be used to identify you, such as anonymous usage statistics, preferences, or other aggregated information.
Collection
: We do
NOT
collect any non-personal information regarding your usage of our apps. Our focus is on providing a seamless user experience without the need for data collection.
3. Location Services:
Collection
: We do
NOT
request, collect, or access your location information. Our apps are designed to function fully without needing to know your geographical location.
Third-Party Apps/Links
Ads and Links
: Our applications and services do
NOT
display advertisements or links to third-party companies or mobile applications. We maintain a clean and focused user interface without external distractions.
Security
Data Handling
: We do not store, collect, or retain any information from our users. This ensures that your data remains entirely within your control.
Protection
: Since we do not gather any data, there is no risk of data breaches or unauthorized access to your personal information through our apps.
Your Privacy
Commitment
: We are committed to protecting your privacy. By not collecting any personal or non-personal information, we ensure that your usage of our watch face applications is entirely private and secure.
User Identity
: We do not store or retain any personal information that can be used to identify you, ensuring complete anonymity and privacy in your interactions with our apps.
Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns regarding our privacy practices, please do not hesitate to contact us at ndwatchfaces[at]hotmail.com. We are dedicated to maintaining transparency and addressing any issues you may have.
This Privacy Policy outlines our dedication to preserving the privacy and security of our users. Your trust is paramount, and we strive to provide a safe and private experience through our watch face applications.